The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for network resource management in the context of 5G cellular networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper extensively discusses the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses system-level optimization, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses security and privacy concerns, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper discusses resource allocation and management, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
